ng the visible end-margin wall Janis reported. v7 (2026-07-15, R-111 territory): root-caused and fixed the actual "reads solid with lid open" defect (`fixed_shell_profile()`'s own fake diagonal closing edge). Full per-version detail lives in each BBQ-chambers-vN.scad's own header, PART_MANIFEST.md, SKELETON_WORKSHEET.md, and cc_chat_log.md — not restated here, per this file's own WHAT/WHERE-only scope. GOVERNANCE FLAG (2026-07-13, still open): design_scope_of_work_rule.md/SKELETON_WORKSHEET.md content partially cc/Claude-Web-reconstructed, not verbatim Janis-confirmed — see PENDING DESIGN DECISIONS (rules-dimensions.md) |
